          <h2 id="when-to-incorporate">When to Incorporate Your Airbnb Business</h2>
          <p>Incorporation is not automatically the right move. The key question is whether your Airbnb generates more profit than you need to live on. If you're spending every dollar of Airbnb income on personal expenses, incorporation provides limited tax benefit because you'd need to pay yourself a salary or dividends anyway, triggering personal tax rates.</p>

          <p>The math becomes compelling when you're retaining profits inside the business. Here's a simplified example:</p>

