          <h3>CRA Record Keeping: The 6-Year Rule</h3>
          <p>The CRA requires you to keep all records supporting your tax return for a minimum of six years from the end of the tax year they relate to. For Airbnb hosts, this means:</p>

          <ul>
            <li><strong>Income records:</strong> Airbnb annual earnings summaries, bank statements showing all deposits</li>
            <li><strong>Expense receipts:</strong> Every receipt for cleaning supplies, repairs, furniture, professional fees</li>
